            text = "geven in Oysh- dos veyst men, m'hot gerufn tsu UNK. fun Mishkolts hot men gefirt oyf Oyshvits, un fun Oyshvits hot men gefirt dort ahin tsu arbetn dortn," 
        intervals [491]:
            xmin = 1584.773 
